ill be run publicly, <PERSON> Kozlowski </PERSON> said, unlike the past when the names of all members but the chairman were kept secret. Viewers say news reports have become more even-handed in recent months, and one satirical program even poked fun at communsit President <PERSON> Wojciech </PERSON> <PERSON> Jaruzelski </PERSON> _ something that would have been unthinkable a year ago.
